	dependency.

	Doc processors (lib/*mm-2.4/proc) moved gtkmm2.4-shlibs ->
	gtkmm2.4 as of 2.6.4-1, then moved gtkmm2.4 -> gtkmm2.4-dev as
	of 2.6.14-2/1002

	Misc other docs and things used by things that use gtkmm moved
	gtkmm2.4 -> gtkmm2.4-dev as of 2.6.14-2/1002
